Detailed Description

template<typename Node, typename Get_key, typename Compare = Lt_functor<typename Get_key::Key_type>>
class cxx::Avl_tree< Node, Get_key, Compare >

A generic AVL tree.

Parameters:
Node the data type of the nodes (must inherit from Avl_tree_noed).
Get_key the meta fcuntion to get the key value from a node. The implementation uses Get_key::key_of(ptr_to_node).
Compare binary relation to establish a total order for the nodes of the tree. Compare()(l, r) must return true if the key l is smaller than the key r.
Examples:

tmpfs/lib/src/fs.cc.

Pair< Node *, bool > cxx::Avl_tree< Node, Get_key, Compare >::insert ( Node *  new_node  ) 

Insert a new node into this AVL tree.

Parameters:
new_node a pointer to the new node. This node must not already b in an AVL tree.
Returns:
A pair, with second set to 'true' and first pointing to new_node, on success. If there is already a node with the same key that first point to this node and second is 'false'.
